<h1 id="china-unicom-mascot-design">China Unicom Mascot Design</h1>

<p>Wow brand is a communications industry brand launched by China Unicom in 2009.
Connotation of Wow brand: Wow brand and Internet partners are working on a deeper integration to serve people enjoing the online life anytime and anywhere, with faster network and better
experience. Wow brand opens up new ways to play an lets the fun extend.
Based on the brand connotation, I designed a cartoon character called Wow bean who is good at having fun with people and provides latest technology.</p>

